OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FCooper made his screen debut in
OL,8,FAdolescence, which was released on
OL,9,FNetflix in 2025, and saw him play the
OL,10,Frole of Jamie Miller, a 13-year-old
OL,11,Faccused of murdering a classmate.
OL,13,FEsther said it was "unbelievable" that
OL,14,FCooper has now won a Golden Globe as
OL,15,Fwell as winning a Critic's Choice
OL,16,FTelevision Award, National Television
OL,17,FAward and an Emmy for the role.
